OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,FScotland becoming independent would be
OL,7,Fa "win" for Vladimir Putin, a UK
OL,8,Fdefence minister has said.
OL,10,FDefence procurement minister Luke
OL,11,FPollard was speaking to Scottish
OL,12,Fjournalists in London on Tuesday when
OL,13,Fhe hit out at the long-standing SNP
OL,14,Fstance of removing nuclear weapons
OL,15,Ffrom Scottish waters if the country
OL,16,Fleaves the UK.
OL,18,FHe also said the Scottish Government's
OL,19,Fposition meant submariners were seeing
OL,20,F"their hard work effectively attacked".
