OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,FA paper released earlier this month by
OL,7,Fthe Scottish Government said a post-
OL,8,Findependence Scotland would enshrine
OL,9,Fthe removal of nuclear arms from the
OL,10,Fcountry in an interim written
OL,11,Fconstitution.
OL,13,F"The thing that Putin fears most about
OL,14,Fthe UK is our nuclear deterrent," the
OL,15,Fminister said.
OL,17,F"So why make the argument that gives
OL,18,FPutin a win? That removes jobs and
OL,19,Fmakes Britain less secure?
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@aO]yD@AOU
