OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,F"I don't think, in an era of threats,
OL,7,Fthat's a credible position."
OL,9,FHe added: "I'm very mindful that the
OL,10,Ffuture of Scotland is very much down
OL,11,Fto the people of Scotland.
OL,13,F"But if I was sat in the Kremlin and I
OL,14,Fwas looking at the nation that is at
OL,15,Fthe forefront of support for Ukraine,
OL,16,Fis at the forefront of support for the
OL,17,FBaltic states, that has a commitment
OL,18,Fto support Ukraine after a peace, and
OL,19,Fthere was a way to erode its defence
OL,20,Fcapabilities, I would regard that as a
OL,21,Fwin."
