OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,FThe minister also hit out at the
OL,7,FScottish Government's reticence to
OL,8,Finvest public money in defence.
OL,10,FIn September, John Swinney announced
OL,11,Fhis Government would shift to ensure
OL,12,Ffunding was not given to arms
OL,13,Fcompanies who had dealings with states
OL,14,Fcredibly accused of genocide, bringing
OL,15,Fto an end a long-standing position of
OL,16,Fnot providing funding for the
OL,17,Fmanufacturing of munitions.
OL,19,FThe Government, he said, was "on a bit
OL,20,Fof a journey" regarding their defence
OL,21,Fstance.
