OL,6,F"We're very clear that defence is an
OL,7,Fengine for growth," the minister said.
OL,9,F"These are good, well-paid jobs in
OL,10,Fdefence and it is a surprise to me
OL,11,Fevery day that we're not seeing the
OL,12,FScottish Government lean into the
OL,13,Fopportunities that exist, not just on
OL,14,Fthe Clyde but on the east coast as
OL,15,Fwell around Rosyth to create more jobs
OL,16,Fin defence."
