OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,FSNP defence spokesperson Dave Doogan
OL,7,FMP said: "It is unbelievably crass
OL,8,Fthat a Labour minister is using
OL,9,FPutin's illegal invasion of Ukraine as
OL,10,Fa political attack. He should do the
OL,11,Fright thing and apologise.
OL,13,F"Successive Westminster governments
OL,14,Fhave committed to billions on nuclear
OL,15,Fbombs while cutting conventional troop
OL,16,Fnumbers. It is conventional defence
OL,17,Fforces that will protect us from the
OL,18,Fthreats we face today ` not weapons of
OL,19,Fmass destruction on the Clyde.
