OL,3,CScottish independence a 'win for
OL,4,CPutin', defence minister claims
OL,6,F"Scotland has a thriving defence
OL,7,Fsector which saw Norway ` a small,
OL,8,Findependent and nuclear weapon free
OL,9,Fcountry ` choose to build warships
OL,10,Fhere. That in itself speaks volumes
OL,11,Fabout what our country could be
OL,12,Fcapable of through a fresh start with
OL,13,Findependence.
OL,15,F"Scotland's existing multibillion-
OL,16,Fpound annual contribution to UK
OL,17,Fdefence will be far better spent
OL,18,Fequipping an independent Scotland with
OL,19,Fthe personnel and materiel we will
OL,20,Frequire to play our key role in Nato,
OL,21,Fjust like Norway, Finland and Denmark."
